Class SplitInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • filesplitter.model.SplitFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class SplitInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The main data structure of the application. Define a single file to split, its split mode, in how many parts it has to be split or how big it has to be a single part, and eventually the encryption key
    Author:
    Riccardo Rebottini
